## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all possible reasons for abortion. Some sources may have inherent biases based on their organizational goals or the demographic focus of their studies. Additionally, the data may not fully represent the most current trends or reasons due to the varying dates of publication. Further research could provide more comprehensive insights, especially with updated data and broader demographic studies.